participant_id.Description: Unique BIDS identifier for the participant in this study.

iqc_eprime_found.Description: Number of tasks acquired in a session

iqc_eprime_valid.Description: All E-Prime files of the acquired tasks are readable, contain the intended task, and the experiment date & time can be extracted
